<item>
            <title>[HIVE-8666] hive.metastore.server.max.threads default is too high</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-8666</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;hive.metastore.server.max.threads&lt;/tt&gt; defaults to 100K. Each thread requires a 1024KB stack which is 100GB. We should move the default to something more sensible like 1000.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
